<i>noun</i>: 항변 [항ː변], 반박문 [반ː방문], 반박 [반ː박] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>항변 [항ː변]</dt><br>
<dd>counterargument; rebuttal</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 주장에 맞서 옳고 그름을 따짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of arguing over what is right and wrong against another's opinion.</dd><br>
<dt>반박문 [반ː방문]</dt><br>
<dd>refuting statement; refutal; rebuttal</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 의견이나 주장 등에 반대하는 내용을 적은 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A statement of refuting or rebutting a certain opinion, argument, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>반박 [반ː박]</dt><br>
<dd>refutation; rebuttal</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 의견이나 주장 등에 반대하여 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of saying something against a certain opinion, argument, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>